// (A) or does not exists (!A) and combinations thereof.
// 
// | merge mode  | A + B | A + !B | !A + B | !A + !B |
// | ----------- | ----- | ------ | ------ | ------- |
// | REPLACE_ALL | B     | &#xF8;      | B      | &#xF8;       |
// | REPLACE     | B     | A      | B      | &#xF8;       |
// | APPEND      | A, B  | A      | B      | &#xF8;       |
// | PREPEND     | B, A  | A      | B      | &#xF8;       |
// | KEEP        | A     | A      | B      | &#xF8;       |
